{"data":[{"id":564320184,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":307595822,"title":"高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？","question_type":"normal","created":1546272354,"updated_time":1546301579,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"207c9d4703967082299d2e5aa54a944b","url_token":"heng-xing-wu-hen","name":"恒星无痕","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-de6a01fa26ca8396f6cb380bdc9b7f88_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-de6a01fa26ca8396f6cb380bdc9b7f88_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/207c9d4703967082299d2e5aa54a944b","user_type":"people","headline":"不忘初心","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":60,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/564320184","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-8ea6d07c1d4c5889abad0d091676965a_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546352754,"updated_time":1546352754,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"comment_count":1,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e看到知乎上那篇证明的文章被删了、题主本人也注销了账号，还是忍不住扫了一眼，其实众人讨论的“负质数”不是关键，证明的时候立定义是很常见的手段。他所有的问题全集中在逻辑上。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1.证变式一时，原命题用“且”连接，以逆否来证就必然要证每一个分部都为真。而他在转化逆否时将“任意”“属于”都做了改变，这就导致他明明要证所有的偶数都满足该命题，却只用“2”一种情况就代表了所有并列的分部。这个漏洞在后续过程中循环出现了三次。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e2.其实上述逻辑漏洞已经决定这篇证明从根本上翻车了。然而他还存在另一个致命的漏洞。依然拿变式一来举例，这段证明可以概括为：满足6k+2形式的偶数，可表示为形式一（即符合哥德巴赫的形式）或形式二，然后他发现形式二不符合哥德巴赫这一显而易见的事实，于是就把它舍去了？？？既没证明形式一的必然性，也没证明形式二的不合理性，居然就推出了它只能满足形式一？同上，这一错误也被重复了三次。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e（至于全程把“哥德巴赫”写成“歌德巴赫”也确实是个槽点，我觉得这是对数学的不尊敬。）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ePS：其实网上对他的嘲讽有些过了。事实上从他发那篇帖子开始，人们就迫不及待想看到一出打脸的闹剧，最终他也成功沦为了广大网友开年的第一个笑柄。说实话我很佩服这样的人，至少在高中时期就对世界难题抱有野心不是件容易的事，多少人自诩为天才的自负都在从小到大“谦逊”的教育下渐渐流失。“承认平凡”其实比“不可一世”的代价要大得多。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e最后送上陈景润先生的话与君共勉。希望此次事件不会浇灭他对数学的热忱。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-7388ee1fa2d81c20ba21ddc0947e3b90_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"668\" data-rawheight=\"133\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-74b11010f1d78ea1f89fccb032c64837_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"668\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-7388ee1fa2d81c20ba21ddc0947e3b90_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='668'%20height='133'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"668\" data-rawheight=\"133\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-74b11010f1d78ea1f89fccb032c64837_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"668\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-7388ee1fa2d81c20ba21ddc0947e3b90_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-7388ee1fa2d81c20ba21ddc0947e3b90_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-47dc18d2ccda1a1eb4079e3235f16c62_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"709\" data-rawheight=\"497\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-76736f573d48692627af59148b7a9d7d_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"709\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-47dc18d2ccda1a1eb4079e3235f16c62_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='709'%20height='497'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"709\" data-rawheight=\"497\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-76736f573d48692627af59148b7a9d7d_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"709\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-47dc18d2ccda1a1eb4079e3235f16c